description: Demolition of the existing foodstore and redevelopment to provide 3,502 sqm A1 retail use and 661 sqm flexible A1/A3/A4 retail/cafe/bar use, 221 Private Rented Sector (PRS) apartments (C3 Use Class) across Building A and Building B, 90 car parking spaces, associated hard and soft landscaping, new pedestrian access routes through the site and public and private amenity space
